{"tid":2272982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"祖達自爆打機學踢波","createTime":"2020-11-05T11:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T16:26:21.000Z","uid":19552,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ea34d4ff90c01f11418063f7c705ae4f71645f52","tid":2272982,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:44:53.000Z","msg":"上季英超因疫情停擺期間，賽會舉辦了「ePremier League邀請賽」，讓20支球隊各派一代表參賽，透過足球遊戲《FIFA20》決勝負。利物浦代表阿歷山大阿諾特與狼隊代表迪奧高祖達雙雙打入決賽， 短短半小時的賽事，吸引數十萬人次觀看。<br />\n<br />\n祖達即使在上半場尾段先落後，仍一臉冷靜、沒太多起伏，操控球隊在末段追平，再以「黃金入球」奠勝，才振臂高呼，讓人想起他轉會利物浦後，往往可在賽事末段射入關鍵入球。事實上，祖達打FIFA打得出神入化，達到職業電競選手的水平，今年他曾在高手雲集的「Weekend League」錄得30場全勝，該周排行全球第61名。英國3、4月因疫情「全國封鎖」之時，祖達就窩在住處打FIFA，認為對自己在現實中的表現大有幫助。<br />\n除了FIFA，他亦愛好講求戰略、經營管理的《Football Manager》（簡稱FM，中譯：足球經理人），每次隨隊遠行，《FM》都是他消磨時間的法寶，他最愛用低組別球隊去贏得大成就，亦曾在網上分享心得：「我是量入為出的那種領隊、不會亂花錢買人，但有能力的話也會買自己。玩FM令我更了解當領隊的難處，若你跟我一樣，未來想做個領隊，玩《FM》會獲益良多。」"},{"pid":"f3d1d2accb30c16e0cdfed62f3877b084903e30c","tid":2272982,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97563a0a2ddf5292b3045c8c0e162aea0c93c58f","tid":2272982,"uid":248695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:29:46.000Z","msg":"施蒙尼又走漏眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d0ecc8ff12457bd835ff6222a045e025f015f3","tid":2272982,"uid":67225,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"玩FM令我更了解當領隊的難處<br />\n<br />\n呢d球員邊度揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc708b5de03c2a9f02d1eee74bc2c54d8cbd64c","tid":2272982,"uid":312758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:53:42.000Z","msg":"FM堅難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個都話係明日之星，<br />\n又話咩弱勢陣形，戰術克制，士氣高，狀態爆<br />\n<br />\n結果畀人抄0：5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94664cd9e205cdfda3f488193ee29af8c3d58d99","tid":2272982,"uid":19556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"Weekend League」錄得30場全勝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b654c3ddcf7f35dd01b54c1a8fbb122c6631d43","tid":2272982,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"fm學點教波  學唔到踢波技巧"},{"pid":"78556f45c8b5c0b7eb391ede3b25e7660f374cad","tid":2272982,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"30win係真係pro level<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47247df8e8c0d0698422fcd7152c3f2e67cd0e52","tid":2272982,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"94664cd9e205cdfda3f488193ee29af8c3d58d99","tid":2272982,"uid":19556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"Weekend League」錄得30場全勝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:32:00.000Z","msg":"呢個堅勁，我獲獲過唔到3場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0428324d7d4cc1b823f3829559205646263d348","tid":2272982,"uid":118031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47247df8e8c0d0698422fcd7152c3f2e67cd0e52","tid":2272982,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"94664cd9e205cdfda3f488193ee29af8c3d58d99","tid":2272982,"uid":19556,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTim